<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Gaetano Di Mauro — Musicista</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300&family=Bebas+Neue&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #080808;
    --bg2: #0e0e0e;
    --white: #f0ede8;
    --cream: #c8c0b0;
    --accent: #b8963e;
    --accent2: #7a5c20;
    --red: #c0392b;
    --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: none;
  }

  /* CURSOR */
  .cursor {
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: fixed;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease;
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
  }
  .cursor-ring {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(184,150,62,0.5);
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: fixed;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9998;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, width 0.3s, height 0.3s;
  }

  /* GRAIN OVERLAY */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 512 512' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.75' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='1'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.03;
    z-index: 9990;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 2rem 4rem;
    mix-blend-mode: normal;
  }

  nav::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(8,8,8,0.95), transparent);
    z-index: -1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-logo span { color: var(--accent); }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  /* HERO */
  #hero {
    height: 100vh;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding: 0 4rem 5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 80% 30%, rgba(184,150,62,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 60% at 10% 80%, rgba(184,150,62,0.04) 0%, transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #080808 0%, #0a0908 100%);
  }

  .hero-line {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--accent2), transparent);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .hero-line:nth-child(1) { left: 33.33%; }
  .hero-line:nth-child(2) { left: 66.66%; }

  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 900px; }

  .hero-tag {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .hero-tag::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 13vw, 14rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--white);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.5s forwards;
  }

  h1 em {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 0.6em;
    color: var(--cream);
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--cream);
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 420px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.8s forwards;
  }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute;
    right: 4rem;
    bottom: 5rem;
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--cream);
    opacity: 0.5;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease 1.5s both;
  }

  .hero-scroll::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 1px;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--cream), transparent);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 0.5; }
  }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section { padding: 8rem 4rem; }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--line);
    max-width: 100px;
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  #about {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8rem;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--cream);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .stat {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .stat:hover { border-color: var(--accent2); }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* DISCOGRAPHY */
  #discografia {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--bg2);
  }

  .disco-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .release-card {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, border-color 0.3s;
    cursor: none;
  }

  .release-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--accent), transparent);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .release-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .release-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: var(--accent2); }

  .release-year {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .release-cover {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    filter: grayscale(20%);
    transition: filter 0.4s;
  }

  .release-card:hover .release-cover { filter: grayscale(0%); }

  .release-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .release-type {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--cream);
    opacity: 0.6;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* LISTEN */
  #listen {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .listen-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .platforms {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1px;
  }

  .platform-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.8rem 2.5rem;
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--white);
    transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    cursor: none;
  }

  .platform-link:hover {
    background: #141414;
    border-color: var(--accent2);
    transform: translateX(8px);
  }

  .platform-name {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .platform-arrow {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .platform-link:hover .platform-arrow { transform: translateX(8px); }

  .platform-tag {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* SOCIAL */
  #social {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--bg2);
  }

  .social-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .social-card {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--white);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    cursor: none;
  }

  .social-card:hover { background: #111; border-color: var(--accent2); }

  .social-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .social-platform {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .social-handle {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    opacity: 0.5;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  /* PRESS */
  #press {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .press-intro {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .press-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .press-card {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 3.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .press-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent2); }

  .press-card::before {
    content: '\201C';
    position: absolute;
    top: -1rem;
    left: 2rem;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 10rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.08;
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .press-cover {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    filter: grayscale(30%);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .press-quote {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .press-source {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .press-source-name {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .press-score {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .press-score span {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .press-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }  }

  /* CONTACT */
  #contatti {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10rem 4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  #contatti::before {
    content: 'CONTACT';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 22vw;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    white-space: nowrap;
    pointer-events: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .contact-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 8rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .contact-sub {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--cream);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .contact-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1.2rem 3.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: none;
  }

  .contact-btn::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--accent);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .contact-btn:hover { color: var(--bg); }
  .contact-btn:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 3rem 4rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background: #040404;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--cream);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .footer-copy {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    opacity: 0.3;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  /* SCROLL REVEAL */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(40px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
  }

  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* MOBILE */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    section { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    #hero { padding: 0 2rem 4rem; }
    #about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4rem; }
    .social-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; text-align: center; }
    .hero-scroll { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">G<span>.</span>DI MAURO</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">Biografia</a></li>
    <li><a href="#discografia">Discografia</a></li>
    <li><a href="#press">Press</a></li>
    <li><a href="#listen">Ascolta</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contatti">Contatti</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-line"></div>
  <div class="hero-line"></div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-tag">Musicista · Produttore · Compositore</p>
    <h1>Gaetano<em>Di Mauro</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Musicista, compositore e produttore catanese. Dall'ambient all'elettronica, dalla chitarra alla computer music. Ultimo lavoro: <em>Lampranthus</em> — 2025.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-scroll">Scorri</div>
</section>

<section id="about">
  <div class="about-text reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Biografia</div>
    <h2>Suono come linguaggio</h2>
    <p>Gaetano Di Mauro è un musicista, compositore e produttore catanese. Appassionato di musica fin da bambino, ha iniziato a suonare la chitarra nel 1997, prima da autodidatta e poi al CESM di Catania. Le sue influenze spaziano da Pink Floyd e Pat Metheny a Miles Davis, Ennio Morricone e John Williams.</p>
    <p>La sua discografia conta undici pubblicazioni tra album, EP e singoli — dall'ambient classico di <em>Adagio Espressivo</em> (2015) fino ai recenti <em>Rinse</em> e <em>Lampranthus</em> (2025), passando per concept album come <em>Television</em> e collaborazioni come <em>Interplay</em> con Antonino Cortese.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="about-stats reveal">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number">10+</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Anni di carriera</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number">12</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Pubblicazioni</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number">CT</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Catania, Sicilia</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number">7K</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Ascoltatori / mese</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="discografia">
  <div class="section-label reveal">Discografia</div>
  <div class="disco-grid">

    <div class="release-card reveal">
      <div class="release-year">2025</div>
      <img src="59959384_23270227206746
